               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Collection of salām-hymns (fols. 3r-24r), possibly an excerpt from the
                     Horologium
 I-1) Salām-hymn for Mary (fols. 3r-3v) (ChRep 196, no. 91)
                     I-2) Sǝbḥāt-praise for Jesus (fols. 3v-4v)
 I-3) Sǝbḥāt-praise for the
                     Trinity (fols. 4v-5v)
 I-4) Salām-hymn for Mary (fols. 5v-6r)
 I-5)
                     Sǝbḥāt-praise for Jesus (fols. 6r-7r)
 I-6) Sǝbḥāt-praise for the Trinity
                     (fols. 7r-8r)
 I-7) Salām-hymn for Mary (fols. 8r-9r)
 I-8)
                     Sǝbḥāt-praise for Jesus (fols. 9r-10r)
 I-9) Sǝbḥāt-praise for the Trinity
                     (fols. 10r-11r)
 I-10) Salām-hymn for Mary (fols. 11r-12r)
 I-11)
                     Sǝbḥāt-praise for Jesus (fols. 12r-13v)
 I-12) Sǝbḥāt-praise for the
                     Trinity (fols. 13v-14r)
 I-13) Salām-hymn for Mary (fols. 14r-15r)
                     I-14) Sǝbḥāt-praise for Jesus (fols. 15r-16r)
 I-15) Sǝbḥāt-praise for the
                     Trinity (fols. 16r-17r)
 I-16) Salām-hymn for Mary (fols. 17r-18v) (ChRep
                     196, no. 92)
 I-17) Sǝbḥāt-praise for Jesus (fols. 18v-19v)
 I-18)
                     Sǝbḥāt-praise for the Trinity (fols. 19v-20v)
 I-19) Salām-hymn for Mary
                     (fols. 20v-22v)
 I-20) Sǝbḥāt-praise for Jesus (fols. 22v-23v)
 I-21)
                     Sǝbḥāt-praise for the Trinity (fols. 23v-24r)
 I-22) Sǝbḥāt-praise for God
                     (fol. 24r)</summary>

